Hacking Kya Hai-(What Is Hacking) Hacking Ek aisa tarika hai jise ham Internet ki banayi security system ko todke usme apne hisaab se kuch bhi galat ya sahi changes kar sakte hai.Jaise ki system ko access karna matlab ke system ko apne kabu me karke usme viewing,editing,data copying,information ko copy karna,hidden file changes etc.Koi hacker jab hacking karta hai tab uska maksad kuch alag hi karne ka hota hai.Ham hackers ke maksad ko nahi jaan sakte sab hackers ka alag-alag maksad hota hai.Hacker Matlab ke koi banda system ke sath judkar system ke sath kuch aisi harkate karta hai jisse system ko nuksaan hota hai,aise insaan ko Hacker kaha jata hai.Hacker ko ek clever programmer bhi kaha jata hai kyu ki voh computer ki banayi kadi security ko tod sakta hai.

Page kaise Banaye wo aap uski link par click karke jaan sakte hai: About us Contact us privacy &amp; policy Disclaimer Mistake 48:Result Ka wait na karna : Ye to aapne suna hi hoga, sabra ka fal mitha hota hai.. wahi chij yaha lagu hoti hai.. par bhut se blogger ye galti karte hai.. wo kuch bhi blog me dalte hai to unko turant result chaiye, or jab result nahi milta to blog hi band kar dete hai. Blog me kuch bhi change karte hai to uski rank bhi ek dam se improve nahi hoti hai, dhiye dhire badti hai. Mistake 49:Time to time blog ka backup na lena : Blog ka Backup lena bhi bhut jaruri hai, q ki pata nahi kab blog me kuch error aa jaye, ya aapke hath kuch Mistake ho jaye ya Hack ho jaye, to blog ko wapas start karne ke liye pura data to hona hi chaiye, taki blog par kigai mhenat barbad naa jaye. Mistake 50:War-war permalink change karna : agar aap apni post ka permalink change karte ho aur old link se use open karte ho to 404 error aayega, isliye link set karte time dhiyan rakhe, or agar fir bhi jaruri ho to usko 301 redirect kare new URL par. WordPress me 404 erro kaise tikh kareuski jankari yaha hai. Mistake 52:Apne aap me confidenceka na hona : self confidence &#8211; hame apne uper vishvas rakhna chahiye ki ham ye karenge to iska result 100% hame milega.

Bhut log kya karte hai SEO ka acha knowlage hone ke karan apne kisi bhi article ko search me rank dila dete hai, par wo user ke hisab se galat hai or isko Blank Hate SEO khete hai.Search Engines aesi chijo se bachne ke liye apneAlgorithm me update karte rhete hai jeseHummingbird and Penguins jisme jo bhi aese blank hat Technics use karte hai unki sitesearch engine spam me dal deta hai.Q: SEO kitne Type ke hote hai?A: SEO ko mainly 2 hisso me bata gaya hai, On-Page SEO or Off-Page SEO.On-Page SEO: jitna bhi Search Engine Optimization karte hai ham Post me usko onpage SEO khete hai.Off-Page SEO: apni site ke aalawa jitna bhi SEO karte hai wo off page seo khelata hai.Q: SEO ki kitni Techniques hoti hai?A: SEO ki 2Techniques hoti hai: White Hat SEO or Blank Hat SEO.White Hat SEO: website ko search me lane ke liye jo sahi tarike se SEO kiya jaye usko White Hat SEO khete hai.Black Hat SEO: SEO me kuch ulta sikha karke search engine ko confuse karke website ko searchme lana, usko Blank Hate SEO khete hai.Q: Back Link Kya hoti hai?A:Back link wo hoti hai jab kisi dusri website par hamari website ki link add ho.

Aap meri steps ko follow kare.Step 1: Blogger.com me Login kare fir apne Blog ke Deshboard me jayeStep 2: ab hame Blogger ke Layout ke section me jana hai.Step 3: layout me aane ke baad, Jaha aapko Popular Posts Widget ko add karna hai wha par Layout me Add a Gadget par click kare.Step 4: Ab ek Popup Window khulegi, jisme bhut se widget ki list hogi jo ham apne blog me add kar sakte hai.. Scroll Down karke Popluar Posts Widget par click kare.Step 5: Ab Popular Posts Widget ki setting ka Page aayega.. Usme aap kesa dikhana chate hai blog me aesi setting kare.Widget ka Title de.. Popular Post Top Post Top News kuch bhi de sakte ho, ya fir khali bhi rakh sakte hai.Konsi Popular Post dikhani hai..Pure Time se jo Popular post hai uske liye All time select kare.Pichle 30 din ki popular post dikhane ke liye Last 30 days select kare.Pichle 7 din ki popular post dikhne ke liye Last 7 days select kare.image thumbnail: agar aap apni post ki image bhi dikhana chate hai to tik karde.snippt: Post ke title ke sath starting ki kuch line bhi dikhana chate hai widget me to isko tik kare.Widget me kitni Popular Post dikhana chate hai wo select kare.Puri setting karne ke baad Save ki button par click karke save karde.AB aap apne blog ko Open karke dekhe Widget dikhne laga hoga or jo aapke blog ki popular post hai wo bhi usme dikhne ladi hogi.

Strong Wifi Network Android Mobile Se Wifi Hack Karne Ke Liye 8 Best Android Applications Aaj me wifi hacking apps ke bare me batane wala hu uska use kar ke lakho logo ne free internet ka maza liya hai.Or kuch logo ko in apps ka use karne par bhi free internet ka maza nahi mila hai.Uski bahot si vajah ho sakti hai jaise ki,Mobile root nai hai,Wifi signals weak hai,Wifi network kuch zyada hi secure condition me hai etc.Lekin in sabhi me se jo top par hai voh hai ki Bina Mobile ko root kiye log free wifi pana chahte hai.Lekin boss me sidha bata du ki 100% me se sirf 20% possibility hai ki aapko without root ke wifi password mil sake.Isliye agar aap sach me in apps ka use kar ke wifi hack karna chahte hai toh sab se pehle apne phone ko root kar lijiye.

tkai jab koi search kare to google hamari site ko search result me dikhaye. SEO Kitne Prakar ke hote hai ? SEO ka matlab to aap samaj gaye, ki site ko search engine achi se samaj sake uss trha se teyar karna.. par isme bhi bhut si chije aati hai.. par agar ham isko main 2 part me dekhte hai: On Page SEO Off Page SEO #1 On Page SEO On Page SEO kya hai, wo aapko thoda to uske naam se hi samaj aa gaya hoga.. On Page SEO ka matlab hai wo SEO jo hame hamari site ke page par hi karna hai jisse search engine usko samaj sake ki uske kya hai or usko search me dikhaye. On Page SEO kaise karte hai uske ware me detail me har ek point ko bataya huaa hai, aap usko jarur read kare.. q ki agar aapko ON Page SEO kya hai samaj aa gaya or usko kaise karte hai to aapka 60% kaam to bina mhenat ke ho jayega. On Page SEO me kya hota hai: Title Meta description permalink Keyword Internal Link Content length Image optimize Site loading speed Ye sab On Page SEO me aate hai, inka kya matlab hai or kaise inka use hai wo sab aapko SEO Page SEO ki post me mil jayega. #2 Off Page SEO Off Page SEO kya hai wo bhi aap naam se samaj gaye goge, matlab wo SEO jo Page se hatkar karna hai.. Matlab site par jo bhi dalna tha, jo bhi setting karni thi wo sab ON Page SEO me kardi.. khene ka matlab wo sab kuch jisse site search me me aaye or jo site se bhar ho wo Off Page SEO hota hai. Off Page SEO kya hai or wo kaise karte hai uski detail Post bhi aapko HMH.pe mil jayegi, aap On Page SEO ko sikhne ke baad Off Page SEO ko bhi achi se samje. Off Page SEO me kya kya hota hai: Backlink (High Quality Backlink) Social Signal Guest Post Link Exchange Paid Promotion <a title="Web Directory Kya Hai ?

simple aapko isme apni website or page ka URL dalkar check karna hai.bots crawl kar pa rahe ke nahi site ko ?Search engine Bots site ko crawl karte hai uske baad hi site ko search me dikhagaya jata hai, aese me ye bhi ho sakta hai galti se robots.txt se aapne bots ko block kar diya ho or search engine aapki site ko crawl hi nahi kar pa rahe ho.Robot.txt me to koi gadwad nahi hai wo aap Google ke Free Robots Testing Tool me dekh sakte hai.Step 2: Check Google Algorithm UpdatesTraffic achanak loss hone ka ye bhi ek karan ho sakta hai google me koi bada algorithm update kiya ho, uski jankari ke liye online kuch popular blog hai waha dekh sakte hai.Sabse best tarika kisi bhi update ko pata katne ka twitter hai, q ki yaha aapko sabhi top seo mil jayege.Ab Twitter par kisi bhi Update ko dekhne ke liye aap simple search kar sakte hai, google algorithm update jese aap screenshot me dekh sakte hai.Step 3: Google Search Console Check kareGoogle Search console me aapne apni site ko to add kiya hi hoga, agar nahi kiya hai to abhi add kare wo bhut jaruri hai.Jab bhi koi update aata hai or uski baja se site par koi bhi dikkat hoti hai to waha hame error message mil jata hai, or ham unke bataye tarike ko follow karke usko sahi kar sakte hai.Aap Search console me check kare kahi koi error to nahi aa rahi hai aapki site ko crawl karne me, or ye bhi check kare aapki site ki kitni post index hai.Google Search Console important settings karna bhi jaruri hai, agar aapne abhi tak nahi ki to wo bhi jarur kare.Step 4: Google Analytics me Check karewebsite ki traffic kam hone ka karan aap google analytics se bhi laga sakte hai, aap site ka google analytics open karke uska traffic graph dekhe, isse aapko bhut si jankari mil jayegi.Jese example: google ka ek update aaya tha jisme mobile friendly site ko top par dikhate hai, to aese me agar aap google analytics me dekhte to aapki computer ki traffic to same rheti par agar aapki site mobile friendly nai hoti to aapki mobile ki traffic kam hoti.Iss trha ki bhut si chijo ko dekh kar bhi aap google analytics se pata laga sakte hai, akhir traffic kam hone ka karan kya hai.Agar aapne Google analytics add nahi kiya hai to abhi kare, Google Analytics kaise add kare site me uski jankari yaha di hui hai.Step 5: Check Site SpeedWebsite ki speed ek ranking factor hai google me, or agar aapki site ki speed slow hai to ye bhi ek main karan ho sakta hai aapki traffic ka achanak kam hone ka.Website ki speed kaise improve kare uski tips mene share ki hai, unko follow kare uske sath agar kuch bhi aesi chije ho jiske karan aapki site ki speed kam ho rahi hai to unko bhi tikh kare.website ki speed check karne ke liye Googles PageSpeed Insights ka use kar sakte hai, isme kaha kya gadwad hai wo bhi pata chal jati hai.Step 6:Check MobileGoogle ne ye saaf kar diya hai, ki Mobile ke liye phele Mobile friendly site hi dikhai jayegi or unko ko jada value di jayegi, to hamare liye ye bhut jaruri hai ki site mobile me achi trha se open ho.blog Mobile me achi trha se open ho uske liye aap ek badi Mobile Friendly Template use kare.website Mobile Friendly hai ya nahi wo aap Google keMobile-Friendly Test tool ki madad se pata kar sakte hai.Step 7: Backlink Check kareBacklink wo link hoti hai jo kisi dusri site par hamari kisi page ki link add ki gai ho.
Apni Online tutor website ki marketing ke liye aap social networking sites use kar sakte hain.

Blogging ke Faide kitne hai wo me phele hi share kar chuka hu, par uske aalawa bhi kuch bate hai jinki [&#8230;] The post Blogging Q Kare Uske 13 Faide [Blogging Benefits] appeared first on Hindi Me Help. Blogging Kya hai or Blogging me Kya hota hai ye Aaj bhut log jante hai par Blogging ke Kya Faide hai or Ham Blogging Q Kare ye baat bhut logo ko clear nahi hai.. Blogging ke Faide kitne hai wo me phele hi share kar chuka hu, par uske aalawa bhi kuch bate hai jinki baja se aapko blogging karni chaiye jo me abhi aapse share kar raha hu. Blogging Q Kare Janiye Uske Benefits #1 Blogging se Paise Kama sakte hai: Agar aap Blogging ke ware me thoda bhut knowledge rakhte hai to aapko pata hi hoga ham Blog bana kar paise kama sakte hai.. Blog se paise kamane ke liye uspar ads lagate hai ya fir Affiliate Marketing se bhi blog ke jariye acha khasa paisa kamaya ja sakta hai. #2 Blogging Aasan hai: Duniya ka wese to koi bhi kaam muskil nahi hai, wass ham jo bhi kaam kar rahe hai us kaam me hame maja aana chaiye, to hame wo muskil lagega hi nahi.. Tikh ussi trha bhut logo ko Blogging me maja aata hai or jinko blogging me maja aata hai unke liye duniya ka sabse aasan kaam ye hi hai, Q ki isko puri Duniya ke kisi bhi kone se kar sakte hai. #3 Popularity: Agar Aapka ek Blog hai or aap usme badiya content dalte hai to kuch time me aapko bhut log phechanne lagege. Ek Trha se aap Dusro ke liye misal hoge q ki bhut logo ko to itna hi jaan kar herani ho jati hai ki inki koi website hai.. Q ki unko ye bhi pata nahi hota Website kaise banaye jo ki bhut aasan hai #4 Blogging hame Acha Insan Banati hai: Jo Log kuch time se blogging kar rahe hai aap unse baat karke dekhna, aapko ek alag hi positivity unke andar mhesus hogi.
Step 13: Ab mai aapko Domain or Hosting Dono ko 720 rupay me Kharidne ke baare me Batata hoon.

All About TrueCallerAgar aapne TrueCaller use kiya hai to aapke mind me bhi ye sabal aaya hoga ki TrueCaller number ki detail lata kaha se hai or ye work kaise karta hai.Truecaller ka kaam karne ka tarika bhut simple hai, wo kisi bhi number ki detail batane ke liye uske database me uss number ko search karta hai.. or jesa ki mene bataya 300+ crore se jada number ki detail truecaller ke pass hai.Truecaller jo number ki detail collect karta hai unke kuch tarike hai, jinki madad se wo pata karte hai ki konsa number kon use kar rahe hai.Social Media: Truecaller number ko Social Media par search karta hai, jese Facebook, Twitter.. agar uss number se koi account hai to wo naam truecaller bata deta hai.TrueCaller App: jo log Truecaller App use karte hai unka uspar account banta hai, iss trha truecaller ke pass unki detail aa jati hai..Contact Book: Truecaller App use karne par wo hamare Phone me save contact ko bhi read kar sakte hai, iss trha hamare phone me jitne bhi number save hai unki detail bhi truecaller ke pass chali jati hai.Direct Submit: Truecaller me direct kisi number ko bhi submit kar sakte hai or uska name suggest kar sakte hai.To ab aapko ye to clear ho gaya hoga ki Truecaller number ki detail lata kaha se hai.. To ab aage se kabhi bhi kisi ko call kare to ye naa soche ki aapka number unke pass save nahi hai to wo pata nahi kar payege ki aap kon ho..Aapka jo Mobile number hai wo aapne Social Media par to use kiya hoga, ya kisi aese user ke mobile me save hoga jo Truecaller use karte hai ya aap khud Truecaller App use karte hai.

Par agar aapne kabhi MLM try kiya ho to aapko bhi pata hoga, MLM me ham Long tarm tak kaam nahi kar sakte.. aesa hi Sandeep Masheshwari ke sath huaa.. Unhone bhi usko chor diya. MLM company ko to unhone chor diya, par jitne time tak wo usme kaam kar rahe the, usme unhone bhut si chije sikhi, or sambe main baat jab wo MLM kar rahe the to unhone Marketing ki bhut books bhi padhi. Marketing ka unko itna knowledge ho gaya tha ki unhone, Marketing ke upar ek Book bhi likh di, lekin Book bhi ek Failure hi sabit hui. Jo sandeep maheshwari book likhi thi, uski bhi ek khas baat thi, wo ulti open hoti thi matlab piche se or uske sabse phele Page par hi likha tha agar aap apne padhne ka tarika nahi badal sakte, to aap apni soch ko kaise badal sakte ho. Ye jo Book likhi, Marketing ke upar bhale wo success nahi hui, par usko likhne se jo Sandeep Maheshwari ko mila wo sabse badke tha.. Q ki unhone ek book likhne ke chakkar me pata nahi kitni marketing ki book badh dali, jisse unko marketing ka acha khasa knowlage ho gaya. Sandeep Ka Interest Modeling me bhi tha, to unhone in sab ke baad modelingme try karne ka socha or apna ek portfolio banbaya, Yaha bhi unhe bhut si problem ka samna karna padha q ki koi bhi acha Photographer 50 hajar ke aas pass charge karta hai ek portfolio ke jo ki unke liye bhut jada tha.. Fir bhi jese tese banbaya or try kiya par usme bhi unko koi acha response nahi mila. Ab Sandeep ne socha jo mere jese Models hai jo Paise ke karan apnaportfolio nahi banwa pa rahe hai, me unki help karu orportfolio banao, or unhone Camera leke ye kaam start kiya.

May 26, 201749Facebook Twitter Google+ WhatsApp PinterestHello Bloggers, Aaj ham is Post me dekhege kaise apni Post me Youtube Video ko add karte hai.Me phele hi bata chuka hu ki ham video ko direct post editor sekaise add kar sakte hai, is post me, jisme mene Post editor ke sare option ke bare me batya hai..Sayad aapko pata hi hoga ki ham youtube se bhi badiya paise kama sakte hai, or agar hamara blog bhi hai to usse hamare video ke views to badege hi sath hi sath income bhi badegi.. blog or Youtube dono ki.Start karne ke phele mesamajta hu aapne apna video youtube me upload kar diya hai, or agar aap koior ka video add karna chate hai to wo bhi kar sakte hai.Youtube Video ko add karne ke liye phele hame Youtube Video ka Embed code lena hoga fir ham usko Apne Blog ke HTML me daal kar Video Add kar sakte hai.Youtube Video ka HTML EmbedCode kaise leSabse phele aap jis video ko add karna chate hai usko youtube me khole..Ab niche aap dekhege Share ka Option hai, uspar click kare, Fir Embed par click kareAb ek code aa jayega jisko ham kahi bhi HTML me add karke video ko add kar sakte hai.Agar aap video ko apne hisab se customize karna chate hai to aap SHOW MORE par click kare.Ab kuch or Option aayege, jinko ham apne video me set kar sakte hai.Video Size Aap jo video hai uska kya size rakhna chate hai usko select kar sakte hai.Show Suggested Video isko agar aap Tik karte hai to Video khatam hone ke baad jo Video ka suggestion aate hai wo aayege.Show Player Control Is option me jo Video player ke option hai, Play, Volume , settings wo nahi dikhege.Show Video Title Agar aap Video ka Title dikhana chate hai to isko tik kare.Enable Privacy is option tik karne par youtube hamare visitor ko jab tak track nahi karega jab tk wo video ko play nahi karte.
